ðŸ“¦ 3. Data Pipeline (How Metrics Are Collected & Used)

[AKS / Azure Resources]
        â”‚
        â”œâ”€â–º Prometheus (Pod, Node, Cluster)
        â”œâ”€â–º Azure Monitor API (Infra)
        â”œâ”€â–º Azure Cost Mgmt API (Cost)
